'''Bllaɣɣu''' <ref>https://amawal.net/blla%C9%A3%C9%A3u?l=tz_MA</ref>(s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tsrɣint]] : المني) iga aḥruray umlil dadd issufuɣ urgaz sg [[Aglay|uglay]] ns akud nna iskar [[tuqqut]] d kra n tmɣart nɣ d kra yaḍni nɣ akud nna ittqqu d kra n tɣarast yaḍni. Blaɣɣu iga aḥruray n tirwit dar akk imaddarn. 

== Aklu ==
Bllaɣɣu iẓẓḍaṛ a ig umlil, amɣdeddi nɣ awkk awraɣ g kra n tikkal. Akud nna iwḍn ufgan iẓẓḍaṛ add ffɣn idammn d bllaɣɣu ma t ittadjan a dars ili uklu azggaɣ nɣ azwawaɣ. 

